Timeout Pro 隐私政策
Timeout Pro 尊重用户的隐私。本隐私政策旨在说明我们如何收集、使用和保护您的信息。
1. 信息收集
Timeout Pro 不会收集任何可识别个人身份的信息。应用使用您的摄像头和本地存储来完成视频拍摄和保存，所有视频均仅保存在您的设备中。
2. 信息使用
我们不会与任何第三方共享您的信息，也不会用于广告或跟踪。
3. 相机与媒体访问
为实现视频拍摄功能，Timeout Pro 需要访问您的摄像头和相册。本应用不会在未经许可的情况下访问这些资源。
4. 数据安全
所有数据均保存在用户本地设备上，不会上传至我们的服务器。
5. 联系方式
如有任何隐私相关问题，请联系我们：timeoutpro@outlook.com

Timeout Pro Privacy Policy
Timeout Pro respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.
1. Information Collection
Timeout Pro does not collect any personally identifiable information. The app uses your camera and local storage to record and save videos. All videos remain on your device.
2. Information Use
We do not share any data with third parties and do not use it for advertising or tracking.
3. Camera & Media Access
Timeout Pro requires access to your camera and photo library to enable video recording. It does not access these without permission.
4. Data Security
All data is stored locally on your device and is never uploaded to our servers.
5. Contact
For any privacy-related inquiries, contact us at timeoutpro@outlook.com

Last Updated: October 3, 2025
